Initial Condition
reset = 1 → System in IDLE
Pump = OFF

Low Level (water_sensor_low = 1)
State → LOW_LEVEL
Pump → ON ✅

Mid Level (water_sensor_mid = 1)
State → MID_LEVEL
Pump → ON ✅

High Level (water_sensor_high = 1)
State → HIGH_LEVEL
Pump → OFF ❌

State Transition Flow
IDLE → LOW → MID → HIGH
HIGH → MID → LOW → IDLE

| Water Level | State      | Pump |
| ----------- | ---------- | ---- |
| Low         | LOW_LEVEL  | ON   |
| Mid         | MID_LEVEL  | ON   |
| High        | HIGH_LEVEL | OFF  |
